---
title: Cal Smart Chicken Patties in Tikka Sauce with Parsley Rice
description: Flecks of cilantro stems don't just make these chicken patties look pretty, they also add a ton of flavour! Tikka sauce blends beautifully with cream cheese to give this curry a velvety texture without the heaviness.

